attributes.review:
First of all, this app is very buggy. Often times when it starts up, it just gets in a loop with content talking about the previous app. It doesn’t even attempt to tell you why this version of the app is better. 

Second, this app constantly lies about how much data it uses and the things it will give you. 

Thirdly, although it seems like a USA app, I’m pretty sure all the coding was done in Russia. Lots of typos and bad grammar.
